history.title: Seneca College
history.subtitle: Student
history.content: This three-year advanced diploma program provided me with the skills and knowledge to begin my career as a developer. I learned programming languages, program design and system analysis. Web concepts were integrated into all the courses to develop active database web programs on a variety of operating systems. Advanced techniques were taught through professional option courses.
